       whether it has that property, which crashes WinUI's x:Uid resource application at
       InitializeComponent time (confirmed on-device — see DECISIONS.md's second T-F05 follow-up,
       "correction" note). Keep pending-list (Button) and browse-mode (TextBlock) headers under
       fully separate key names even when the display text is identical. -->
